commit.message:
Fix a timeout overflow bug in 32-bit machines

Use "sys.maxsize" to override unlimited timeouts, instead of the definite number "2**31" that can lead to overflows.

commit.message:
Adjust two bare except: clauses to appease flake8

This fixes the final two flake8 errors that are causing CI to fail. In
both cases, catching a fairly broad class of exceptions makes sense, but
neither case needs to handle SystemExit or similar exceptions (as far as
I can tell).

Signed-off-by: Jeremy Cline <jcline@redhat.com>

Fix the flake8 errors in test_api.py

This fixes three flake8 error that are causing CI failures. The first
two fix an ambiguous variable name, and the last one catches the
specific exception being raised.

Signed-off-by: Jeremy Cline <jcline@redhat.com>
